v2.0: Add multi-turn conversations and persistent history

Major features:
- Multi-turn conversation support with full context
- localStorage persistence (max 20 conversations)
- Conversation history UI with sidebar
- Auto-generated titles and relative timestamps
- New/Clear conversation buttons
- Thread tracking and message history display

Technical changes:
- Backend: Send full message history for agent context
- Backend: Enhanced thread ID extraction from trace spans
- Backend: Omit thread fields for new conversations (fixes 401)
- Frontend: Complete rewrite with localStorage management
- Frontend: Conversation switching and history rendering
- Frontend: Extract text from events for context building

Bug fixes:
- Fixed: "Thread 0 does not exist" error (omit fields for new convos)
- Fixed: Agent doesn't remember context (send full message history)
- Fixed: Thread IDs not extracted (parse trace attributes)

Documentation:
- Rewrote README.md and DEPLOYMENT.md (generic, comprehensive)
- Updated CHANGELOG.md with implementation details
- Added TESTING.md with 12 test scenarios
- Added RELEASE_NOTES_v2.0.md

Breaking changes: None (backwards compatible)

